OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772917555
OL,3,CRussia gave Iran intel to help strike
OL,4,CUS military, officials suggest
OL,6,FRussia has provided Iran with
OL,7,Finformation that could help Tehran
OL,8,Fstrike American warships, aircraft and
OL,9,Fother assets in the region, according
OL,10,Fto two officials familiar with US
OL,11,Fintelligence on the issue.
OL,13,FThe officials, who were not authorised
OL,14,Fto comment publicly and spoke on the
OL,15,Fcondition of anonymity, cautioned that
OL,16,Fthe US intelligence has not uncovered
OL,17,Fthat Russia is directing Iran on what
OL,18,Fto do with the information.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
