OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772917555
OL,3,CRussia gave Iran intel to help strike
OL,4,CUS military, officials suggest
OL,6,FIt comes as US and Israel continue
OL,7,Ftheir bombardment of Iran for an
OL,8,Feighth day, while the Islamic Republic
OL,9,Flaunches retaliatory strikes on Israel
OL,10,Fand at a number of Gulf states allied
OL,11,Fwith the US.
OL,13,FMoscow maintains friendly relations
OL,14,Fwith Tehran, which has faced years of
OL,15,Fisolation internationally over its
OL,16,Fnuclear program and its support of
OL,17,Fproxy groups that have wreaked havoc
OL,18,Fin the Middle East, including
OL,19,FHezbollah, Hamas and the Houthis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
