OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772917555
OL,3,CRussia gave Iran intel to help strike
OL,4,CUS military, officials suggest
OL,6,FWhite House officials downplayed the
OL,7,Freports from officials, but did not
OL,8,Fdeny that Russia was sharing
OL,9,Fintelligence with Iran about US
OL,10,Ftargets in the region.
OL,12,FPress secretary Karoline Leavitt on
OL,13,FFriday told reporters that "it clearly
OL,14,Fis not making any difference with
OL,15,Frespect to the military operations in
OL,16,FIran because we are completely
OL,17,Fdecimating them".
OL,26,@uD@\OUyD@PO]
