OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772917555
OL,3,CRussia gave Iran intel to help strike
OL,4,CUS military, officials suggest
OL,6,FDefence Secretary Pete Hegseth in a
OL,7,FCBS' "60 Minutes" interview on Friday
OL,8,Fsaid the US is "tracking everything"
OL,9,Fand factoring it into battle plans,
OL,10,Fwhen asked about the reports Russia
OL,11,Fwas aiding Iran.
OL,13,F"The American people can rest assured
OL,14,Ftheir commander in chief is well aware
OL,15,Fof who's talking to who," he said.
OL,17,F"And anything that shouldn't be
OL,18,Fhappening, whether it's in public or
OL,19,Fback-channelled, is being confronted
OL,20,Fand confronted strongly."
