OL,3,CRussia gave Iran intel to help strike
OL,4,CUS military, officials suggest
OL,6,FOn Friday evening, President Donald
OL,7,FTrump berated a reporter for raising
OL,8,Fthe matter when he opened the floor to
OL,9,Fquestions from the media at the end of
OL,10,Fa White House meeting about how paying
OL,11,Fstudent-athletes has recalibrated
OL,12,Fcollege sports.
OL,14,F"I have a lot of respect for you,
OL,15,Fyou've always been very nice to me,"
OL,16,FTrump said to Peter Doocy, the Fox
OL,17,FNews reporter. "What a stupid question
OL,18,Fthat is to be asking at this time.
OL,19,FWe're talking about something else."
OL,26,@{D@dO]
