OL,3,CRussia gave Iran intel to help strike
OL,4,CUS military, officials suggest
OL,6,FLeavitt declined to say if Trump had
OL,7,Fspoken to Russian President Vladimir
OL,8,FPutin about the reported intelligence
OL,9,Fsharing or whether he believed Russia
OL,10,Fshould face repercussions, saying she
OL,11,Fwould let the president speak to that
OL,12,Fhimself.
OL,14,FAsked whether Russia would go beyond
OL,15,Fpolitical support and offer military
OL,16,Fassistance to Iran, Kremlin spokesman
OL,17,FDmitry Peskov said there has been no
OL,18,Fsuch request from Tehran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
