OL,3,CRussia gave Iran intel to help strike
OL,4,CUS military, officials suggest
OL,6,F"We are in dialogue with the Iranian
OL,7,Fside, with representatives of the
OL,8,FIranian leadership, and will certainly
OL,9,Fcontinue this dialogue," he said
OL,10,FFriday.
OL,12,FPushed on whether Moscow has provided
OL,13,Fany military or intelligence
OL,14,Fassistance to Tehran since the Iran
OL,15,Fwar's start, he refrained from comment.
OL,17,FRussia has tightened its relationship
OL,18,Fwith Iran as it looked for badly
OL,19,Fneeded missiles and drones to utilise
OL,20,Fin its four-year war against Ukraine.
