OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAsked whether the revelation had
OL,12,Fshaken Trump's faith in Putin's
OL,13,Fability to cut any peace deal in the
OL,14,FRussia-Ukraine war, Leavitt said, "I
OL,15,Fthink the president would say that
OL,16,Fpeace is still an achievable objective
OL,17,Fwith respect to the Russia-Ukraine
OL,18,Fwar."
