OL,3,CRussia gave Iran intel to help strike
OL,4,CUS military, officials suggest
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Ukrainian President
OL,7,FVolodymyr Zelenskyy says the United
OL,8,FStates and its allies in the Middle
OL,9,FEast are seeking Ukraine's expertise
OL,10,Fin countering Iran's Shahed drones.
OL,12,FTehran has been supplying Russia with
OL,13,FShaheds for its war on Ukraine and are
OL,14,Fnow utilizing them in retaliatory
OL,15,Fattacks throughout the Gulf.
OL,17,FZelenskyy says that he's spoken to the
OL,18,FUnited Arab Emirates, Qatar, Bahrain,
OL,19,FJordan and Kuwait about possible
OL,20,Fcooperation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
