OL,3,CRussia gave Iran intel to help strike
OL,4,CUS military, officials suggest
OL,6,F"Ukraine knows how to defend against
OL,7,FShahed drone attacks because our
OL,8,Fcities have faced them almost every
OL,9,Fnight," said Ukraine's ambassador to
OL,10,Fthe United States, Olga Stefanishyna.
OL,11,F"When our partners are in need, we are
OL,12,Falways ready to help."
